Miles pulls at the piñata



This was a string piñata, so the kids had to pull the ribbons instead of hitting it. Miles found the winning ribbon...
Taken Saturday, March 2, 2002.  Original image size: 1600x1200, 977kb
Technical details: Olympus C700UZ, 1/320s @ F3.5, ISO 400, 60mm
